paths: Obvious paths: southeast, south, west, northwest
description: Twin cannon guard the entrances to Jezebelly Plaza and Gunner's Lane, their muzzles crammed with dirt and spikes to prevent an accidental firing.  Heavy traffic passes through frequently, most headed for the Crow's Nest Pub, planning on warming themselves up with the bar's more unusual concoctions.
title: [Spitfire Alley, Tartrunner Row]
